#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&akregator; is a program to read <acronym>RSS</acronym> and other online "
"news feeds."
msgstr ""
"&akregator; je program za branje <acronym>RSS</acronym> in drugih spletnih "
"virov novic."

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
